	measure 'Analysis for CSB Total' = ```
			
			VAR EndDate   = EOMONTH( TODAY(), -1 )
			VAR StartDate = DATE( 2024, 10, 1 )
			RETURN
			CALCULATE(
			    SUM ( ___SSOCC_Data[Value] ),
			    FILTER (
			        ___SSOCC_Data,
			        VAR s = UPPER( TRIM( ___SSOCC_Data[Service/Product] ) )
			        RETURN
			            s IN {
			                "ANALYSIS FOR CSB",
			                "ANALYSIS FOR CRIME SUPPRESSION BUREAU",
			                "CSB ANALYSIS"
			            }
			    ),
			    ___SSOCC_Data[Date] >= StartDate,
			    ___SSOCC_Data[Date] <= EndDate
			)
			
			```
		formatString: 0
		lineageTag: 73a6ce1d-0114-4bd2-af25-8d458cc6e8fc

	measure 'CSB Card Title' = ```
			
