	column 'Period MM-YY' = ```
			
			VAR YearPart = LEFT(___SSOCC_Data[Period], 2)
			VAR MonthPart = RIGHT(___SSOCC_Data[Period], 3)
			VAR MonthNumber = SWITCH(
			    MonthPart,
			    "Jan", "01",
			    "Feb", "02", 
			    "Mar", "03",
			    "Apr", "04",
			    "May", "05",
			    "Jun", "06",
			    "Jul", "07",
			    "Aug", "08",
			    "Sep", "09",
			    "Oct", "10",
			    "Nov", "11",
			    "Dec", "12",
			    "00"
			)
			RETURN MonthNumber & "-" & YearPart
			```
		lineageTag: a0baf73e-e6f8-42c6-bf23-7e3ee464998b
